---
import VoladuraVideo from "@/assets/videos/9..mp4";
---

<section id="servicios-voladura" class="mx-auto w-full py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-32">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Section Header -->
    <div class="mb-12 lg:mb-16">
      <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
        <div
          class="from-golden-yellow-400 to-golden-yellow-500 h-1 w-12 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r"
        >
        </div>
        <span
          class="text-golden-yellow-600 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase"
        >
          Catálogo Técnico
        </span>
      </div>
      <h2
        class="text-green-army-900 mb-4 text-4xl leading-tight font-bold sm:text-5xl"
      >
        Servicios Especializados
        <span class="text-golden-yellow-500 block">de Voladura</span>
      </h2>
      <p
        class="text-bone-white-700 max-w-2xl text-justify text-lg leading-relaxed"
      >
        Cada tipo de voladura requiere un diseño técnico específico. Nuestros
        especialistas adaptan la ingeniería de fragmentación a las condiciones
        geológicas, normativas y operativas de su proyecto.
      </p>
    </div>
    <!-- Gallery -->
    <div class="gallery flex">
      <!-- Left content -->
      <div class="left hidden w-1/2 lg:block">
        <div class="desktopContent m-auto w-4/5">
          <div
            class="desktopContentSection flex min-h-screen flex-col justify-center"
          >
            <div class="flex flex-col items-start justify-center space-y-4">
              <!-- Section Label -->
              <div class="mb-4 flex items-center gap-3">
                <div
                  class="from-golden-yellow-400 to-golden-yellow-500 h-1 w-12 rounded-full bg-linear-to-r"
                >
                </div>
                <span
                  class="text-golden-yellow-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase"
                >
                  Voladuras
                </span>
              </div>
              <h1 class="text-green-army-900 text-2xl font-bold">
                Voladuras a Cielo Abierto para Vías
              </h1>
              <p class="text-bone-white-900 text-justify">
                Diseñamos mallas de perforación y voladura específicas para la
                <span class="font-bold text-green-900"
                  >construcción y ampliación de vías</span
                > y cortes de talud. Nuestro enfoque técnico permite el avance rápido
                en proyectos de autopistas y vías 4G y 5G, controlando la proyección
                de roca para no afectar el entorno operativo.
              </p>
              <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
                <h2 class="text-green-army-900 text-2xl font-bold">
                  Aplicacion:
                </h2>
                <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
                  <li
                    class="bg-green-army-950/80 border-golden-yellow-500/80 text-golden-yellow-300 inline-block rounded-full border px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase backdrop-blur-sm"
                  >
                    Sector Infraestructura
                  </li>
                  <li
                    class="bg-green-army-950/80 border-golden-yellow-500/80 text-golden-yellow-300 inline-block rounded-full border px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase backdrop-blur-sm"
                  >
                    Construcción Vial
                  </li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="desktopContentSection flex min-h-screen flex-col justify-center"
          >
            <h1 class="text-green-army-900 text-2xl font-bold">Green</h1>
            <p>
              Green is a color that is often associated with nature, growth, and
              harmony. It is a calming and relaxing color that can evoke
              feelings of balance, stability, and freshness.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="desktopContentSection flex min-h-screen flex-col justify-center"
          >
            <h1 class="text-green-army-900 text-2xl font-bold">Pink</h1>
            <p class="text-bone-white-900 text-lg">
              Pink is a color that is often associated with femininity, romance,
              and sweetness. It is a softer and more delicate shade of red that
              can evoke feelings of warmth, love, and nurturing.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="desktopContentSection flex min-h-screen flex-col justify-center"
          >
            <h1 class="text-green-army-900 text-2xl font-bold">Blue</h1>
            <p class="text-bone-white-900 text-lg">
              Blue is a color that is often associated with calmness, trust, and
              reliability. It is a peaceful and serene color that can evoke
              feelings of stability, security, and professionalism.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <!-- Right content -->
      <div
        class="right flex h-auto w-full flex-col items-center lg:h-screen lg:w-1/2 lg:justify-center"
      >
        <!-- Mobile content -->
        <div class="mobileContent w-[80vw] lg:hidden">
          <div class="mobilePhoto red mt-10 size-[80vw] rounded-2xl bg-red-500">
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5">
            <h1>Red</h1>
            <p>
              Red is a color often associated with strong emotions such as
              passion, love, and anger. It's a bold and attention-grabbing color
              that can evoke feelings of excitement, warmth, and energy.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mobilePhoto green mt-10 size-[80vw] rounded-2xl bg-green-500"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5">
            <h1>Green</h1>
            <p>
              Green is a color often associated with nature, growth, and
              harmony. It's a refreshing and calming color that can evoke
              feelings of balance, health, and renewal.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mobilePhoto pink mt-10 size-[80vw] rounded-2xl bg-pink-500"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5">
            <h1>Pink</h1>
            <p>
              Pink is a color often associated with femininity, romance, and
              sweetness. It's a softer and more delicate shade of red that can
              evoke feelings of warmth, love, and nurturing.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div
            class="mobilePhoto blue mt-10 size-[80vw] rounded-2xl bg-blue-500"
          >
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5">
            <h1>Blue</h1>
            <p>
              Blue is a color often associated with calmness, trust, and
              reliability. It's a peaceful and serene color that can evoke
              feelings of stability, security, and professionalism.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Desktop content -->
        <div
          class="desktopPhotos relative hidden aspect-video h-[25vw] w-[40vw] overflow-hidden rounded-2xl shadow-2xl lg:block"
        >
          <video
            class="desktopPhoto absolute h-full w-full object-cover"
            autoplay
            muted
            loop
            playsinline
          >
            <source src={VoladuraVideo} type="video/mp4" />
          </video>
          <div class="desktopPhoto green absolute h-full w-full bg-green-500">
          </div>
          <div class="desktopPhoto pink absolute h-full w-full bg-pink-500">
          </div>
          <div class="desktopPhoto blue absolute h-full w-full bg-blue-500">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import { splitScreenAnimation } from "@/scripts/SplitScreenPinningAnimation";

  splitScreenAnimation();
</script>
